    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still got so much life left in it! It runs like a dream and is in great shape for its next adventure. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with regular maintenance, so you can just hop in and go. It's been perfect for my daily commutes and the occasional weekend getaway. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
