      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically stout example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Under the hood, the S54B32 inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The dual-VANOS unit has been serviced to maintain precision timing, and the rod bearings were recently addressed for preventative maintenance. Handling is sharp thanks to the variable M differential lock and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows some light road wear consistent with its 'good' condition, the suspension geometry remains true, and the induction note from the factory airbox is intoxicating. A true driver\u2019s car with the 'big three' maintenance items accounted for.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
